OL,3,CNine-year-old 'seriously injured'
OL,4,Cafter being struck by electric bike
OL,6,FA nine-year-old boy has been left with
OL,7,F"serious" injuries after he was struck
OL,8,Fby an electric bike in Swansea.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Police says it is
OL,11,Finvestigating the incident which
OL,12,Foccurred at around 3.30pm on Friday,
OL,13,F21 June.
OL,15,FThey say the rider failed to stop.
OL,17,FThe boy was said to have been riding
OL,18,Fhis pedal cycle on Ffordd y Brain in
OL,19,Fthe Blaenymaes area of Swansea.
