OL,3,CNine-year-old 'seriously injured'
OL,4,Cafter being struck by electric bike
OL,6,FHe is said to have been hit by an
OL,7,Felectric Sur-Ron or a Talaria-type
OL,8,Fbike that was being ridden from the
OL,9,Fdirection of Pentregethin Road towards
OL,10,FMiddle Road. The force added that the
OL,11,Frider left the scene returning towards
OL,12,Fthe direction of Pentregethin Road.
OL,14,FThe child is said to have required
OL,15,Fsurgery following the incident.
OL,17,FSouth Wales Police is now appealing
OL,18,Ffor anyone who may have information
OL,19,Fabout the incident to get in contact
OL,20,Fwith them.
