OL,3,CNine-year-old 'seriously injured'
OL,4,Cafter being struck by electric bike
OL,6,FIn a statement issued on Monday, 24
OL,7,FJune, the force said: "The collision
OL,8,Fhas been captured on CCTV and there
OL,9,Fare a number of persons who are known
OL,10,Fto be in the area at the time who may
OL,11,Fhave witnessed the rider of the
OL,12,Felectric bike.
OL,14,F"The rider is described as a white
OL,15,Fmale, wearing a black bobble hat, with
OL,16,Fa black and white chequered top with a
OL,17,Fgrey hood, blue tracksuit trousers and
OL,18,Ftrainers.
